OL,3,C'Everything is gone': #50,000 cost to
OL,4,Crepair fishman's boat after sinking
OL,6,FA Guernsey fisherman has told ITV News
OL,7,Fabout the moment his ship started to
OL,8,Fsink - taking his livelihood with it.
OL,10,FMichael Scrimshaw was pulling up crab
OL,11,Fpots off the coast of Sark at the end
OL,12,Fof September, when his equipment
OL,13,Fsnagged and caused his boat to capsize.
OL,15,FHe then found himself in the water,
OL,16,Fand his boat disappearing under the
OL,17,Fwaves.
OL,19,FMichael said: "I was trying to get my
OL,20,Flifejacket on, everything was a
OL,21,Fscramble and a panic, a real panic.
