OL,3,C'Everything is gone': #50,000 cost to
OL,4,Crepair fishman's boat after sinking
OL,6,F"Ropes were everywhere and the boat
OL,7,Fwas on its side rolling over - it's
OL,8,Fjust tragic, everything is gone."
OL,10,FMichael's ship, the Wild Wave, was
OL,11,Fpartially refloated and the Guernsey
OL,12,FCoastguard were able to tow the vessel
OL,13,Fback to St Peter Port.
OL,15,FWhilst the ship looks in good form,
OL,16,FMichael says the damage will be
OL,17,Fexpensive to repair.
OL,19,F"The engine and the electrics are all
OL,20,Fwritten off and all needs to be
OL,21,Freplaced.
