OL,3,C'Everything is gone': #50,000 cost to
OL,4,Crepair fishman's boat after sinking
OL,6,F"To get the boat fit for sea again
OL,7,Fit's about #40,000 or #50,000 with
OL,8,Fmajor changes, and it might not be
OL,9,Fsuitable for the job anymore.
OL,11,F"This is massive on my career. I'm not
OL,12,Fworking at the minute, I'm trying to
OL,13,Fstart up again on Monday to do a
OL,14,Flittle bit with friends - just do what
OL,15,FI can.
OL,17,FSince the incident, the Guernsey
OL,18,Fcommunity has rallied behind the
OL,19,Ffisherman, and has now raised more
OL,20,Fthan #14,000 to help with repairs.
