OL,3,C'Everything is gone': #50,000 cost to
OL,4,Crepair fishman's boat after sinking
OL,6,FBut Michael's heartbreak comes as the
OL,7,FBailiwick's fishing industry is
OL,8,Falready struggling, with falling fish
OL,9,Fstocks, an influx of Octopus
OL,10,Fdecimating shellfish and a lack of
OL,11,Faccess to tuna fishing.
OL,13,FHe says the kindness of strangers is
OL,14,Fthe only way to save his livelihood.
OL,16,F"It's overwhelming really. I never
OL,17,Fexpected none of this.
